        <item>
            <title>Switch 2 瑪利歐賽車世界，新賽場、新玩法與角色陣容搶先曝光</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/18/mariokartworld/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mariokartworld</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/18/mariokartworld/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 18 Apr 2025 06:38:19 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Nintendo Switch 2]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1304123</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>任天堂計劃於 2025 年 6 月 5 日同步推出新主機 Nintendo Switch 2 與全新遊戲《瑪利歐賽車，世界》，遊戲設計以「全球一體」為主軸，帶來前所未見的連貫世界觀。玩家可在城市、海洋、雪山與沙漠間自由馳騁，並透過連線功能展開最多 24 人的跨洲競賽。同時，遊戲亦將支援遊戲語音通話與拍照分享等新功能，並加入多項輔助模式，令不同程度玩家都能輕鬆享受賽車樂趣。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1638screenshot.jpg"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304161" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1638screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1638screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1638screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>遊戲世界採用無縫連接設計，所有賽道均建構於一個巨大世界地圖內，讓玩家從一條賽道自然駛入下一段旅程。新加入的世界賽道包括「瑪利歐兄弟賽道」、「獎盃城市」、「鹽味鎮」、「羅潔塔天文台」、「鬼影電影院」等地點，賽道橫跨高樓城市、河道水都、荒野彎道與幽暗森林。官方同時安排多條經典賽道回歸，如「奇諾比奧工廠」、「碧姬海灘」、「瓦利歐船艦」等。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct249screenshot.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304129" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct249screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct249screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct249screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct141screenshot.jpeg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304130" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct141screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct141screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct141screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct150screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304131" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct150screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct150screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct150screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct20screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304132" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct20screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct20screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct20screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct221screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304133" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct221screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct221screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct221screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct27screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304134" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct27screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct27screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct27screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct237screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304135" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct237screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct237screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct237screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>角色方面，玩家除可選用瑪利歐、路易吉、碧姬、庫巴等熟面孔外，今集亦加入全新角色，例如「慄寶寶」、「加邦」與「乳牛」，每位角色配合不同車輛配置會帶來獨特性能組合，讓玩家自由搭配出最合適組合。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct312screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304143" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct312screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct312screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct312screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct318screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304144" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct318screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct318screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct318screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct320screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304137" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct320screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct320screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct320screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct38screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304136" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct38screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct38screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct38screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct35screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304139" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct35screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct35screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct35screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct259screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304140" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct259screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct259screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct259screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct324screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304141" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct324screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct324screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct324screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct343screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304142" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct343screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct343screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct343screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>遊戲主要分為兩大賽事系統：「大獎賽」與「生存賽」。大獎賽包含「蘑菇盃」、「火焰花盃」、「星星盃」等級別，每組需完成 4 條賽道並累計排名。而生存賽則屬連續長距離挑戰模式，舉行地點遍佈整個遊戲世界，賽道中設有淘汰制度，若未能於指定名次內通過檢查點便會被剔除出局。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct429screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304145" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct429screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct429screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct429screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct419screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304146" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct419screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct419screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct419screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>道具設計仍為比賽逆轉關鍵，遊戲中將提供多款全新裝備，包括可掉落金幣的「黃金龜殼」、讓對手結冰打滑的「冰凍花」、可變大碾壓敵手的「巨大蘑菇」、能跳躍閃避攻擊的「羽毛」、以及神祕魔法效果的「卡美克」。道具影響大，玩家需靈活運用，逆轉局勢。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct639screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304147" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct639screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct639screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct639screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct650screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304148" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct650screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct650screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct650screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct715screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304149" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct715screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct715screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct715screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct713screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304150" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct713screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct713screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct713screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct79screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304151" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct79screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct79screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct79screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct71screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304152" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct71screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct71screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct71screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>任天堂亦為新手玩家加入多項輔助模式，例如「方向盤輔助」可避免駛離賽道、「體感陀螺儀模式」可利用 Joy-Con 傾斜進行操控。此外，「蓄力跳躍」功能可於直線行駛時按住 R 鍵蓄力，放開時角色便會高跳，有助避開陷阱或越過障礙，甚至可瞬間切入捷徑。</p><p>單人模式方面加入「倒轉」功能，玩家可於操作失誤時將個人時間倒回重試，惟其他賽車手仍會照常行駛，形成真實壓力挑戰。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct740screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304153" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct740screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct740screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct740screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct737screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304154" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct737screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct737screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct737screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>多人模式設計進一步升級，單機最多支援 4 人分割畫面，而連線功能則容許最多 8 台 Switch 2 主機連線進行最多 24 人對戰。玩家可以透過遊戲聊天功能語音溝通，也可利用 Nintendo Switch 2 新增的攝影機實時觀看對方表情，一台攝影機最多辨識 4 人臉部，增強互動趣味。</p><p>遊戲還設有「時間挑戰賽」、「團隊對戰」、「VS 模式」與「對戰模式」等多元玩法，當中包括氣球對戰與金幣爭奪戰等娛樂型比賽模式，滿足不同遊戲喜好。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1046screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304155" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1046screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1046screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1046screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1152screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304156" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1152screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1152screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1152screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct117screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304157" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct117screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct117screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct117screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>在自由駕駛模式中，玩家可隨意遊覽世界各地場景，並可於旅途中進行拍照、擺姿勢、加入相框，記錄賽事精彩瞬間。這個世界亦設有「P 開關」任務點，觸發後會出現隱藏面板與金幣，為探索旅程增添挑戰。</p><p>遊戲世界亦設有「耀西快餐」據點，玩家可外帶「衝刺美食」，並有機會換取與料理相關的服裝，自由搭配角色造型，為遊戲加入生活感與樂趣。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1534screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304158" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1534screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1534screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1534screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1510screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304159" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1510screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1510screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1510screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1336screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304160" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1336screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1336screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1336screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>任天堂將推出主機與遊戲同捆包，《瑪利歐賽車，世界》預計與 Nintendo Switch 2 同日發售，為全球玩家展開一場跨地域、超規模的賽車盛典。</p><br /><b>
]]>
