            <title>iPhone + Mac 生態圈 AirDrop 以外的兩機互動方法  10 個你可能忽略小貼士</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/17/iphone-with-mac/software/ios-app/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=iphone-with-mac</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/17/iphone-with-mac/software/ios-app/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 17 Apr 2025 11:18:38 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MAC App]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1302503</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>不少人愛用 Apple，不僅因為其產品規格、性能和設計，更因為其強大的生態系統——iPhone、iPad、Mac 甚至 Vision Pro 之間的無縫互通。這種互通讓 Apple 產品成為「用過就回不去」的存在！雖然 AirDrop 是大家熟知的分享工具，但 Apple 生態還有更多實用功能，可能你還沒發現！以下整合了 10 個超實用的生態技巧，讓你的 iPhone、iPad 和 Mac 配合更高效。</p><h2>預先設定：</h2><p>要啟用下面介紹的功能，首先你需要確保：</p><p>iPhone 和 Mac 登入相同 Apple ID；</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303667" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041651238-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041651238-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041651238.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲需為同一 AppleID</p><p>iPhone 和 Mac 均連接到同一 Wi-Fi 網絡；</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303668" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041651249-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041651249-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041651249.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲連接至同一 Wi-Fi 網絡</p><p>兩邊均已開啟「接手」（Handoff）功能。</p><p>iPhone 開啟接手功能步驟如下：<br />
首先開啟「設定」，選擇「一般」，點擊「AirPlay 與接續互通」，開啟「接手」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303669" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_1-536x580.jpg" alt="" width="536" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_1-536x580.jpg 536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_1.jpg 832w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 536px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲開啟 iPhone 接手功能</p><p>macOS 設定如下：</p><p>開啟「設定」，選擇「一般」，點擊「AirDrop 與接手」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303680" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_2-1-694x471.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="471" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_2-1-694x471.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_2-1.jpg 700w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「AirDrop 與接手」</p><p>開啟「允許在 Mac 和你的 iCloud 裝置之間使用『接手』功能」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303679" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_3-1-694x436.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="436" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_3-1-694x436.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_3-1.jpg 704w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲開啟「允許在 Mac 和你的 iCloud 裝置之間使用『接手』功能」</p><h2>1. 通用剪貼板：跨裝置複製貼上</h2><p>完成預先設定後，現在你可以在 iPhone 上複製文字、圖片或連結，然後直接在 Mac 上貼上，反之亦然。例如你可以在 Mac Safari 上複製網址，然後直接在手機「貼上」，隨即可在手機上繼續閲讀 Mac 上分享的網頁。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303673" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_4-694x279.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="279" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_4-694x279.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_4.jpg 1252w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在 Mac 上複製網址</p><p>現在即可直接在 iPhone 貼上剛才複製的連結。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303676" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_5-536x580.jpg" alt="" width="536" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_5-536x580.jpg 536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_5.jpg 832w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 536px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可直接分享 Mac 上複製的連結</p><p>你也可以從 iPhone 複製文字，然後直接在 Mac 貼上。</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
